author: kdy1
message:
build(turbopack): Update `swc_core` to `v27.0.6` (#80626)

### What?

ChangeLog:
https://github.com/swc-project/swc/compare/swc_core%40v27.0.4...swc_core%40v27.0.6
Also: https://github.com/swc-project/plugins/pull/476

### Why?

We need to apply the `styled-jsx` changes
